data.description: Welcome to your luxurious retreat near the picturesque Blue Ridge Parkway. This stunning mountain property offers an unparalleled blend of elegance, comfort, and natural beauty, promising a lifestyle of tranquility. Situated on a 3.07 acre tract, this magnificent property boasts a private pond, inviting you to unwind and immerse yourself in the serene surroundings. Whether you're enjoying a leisurely paddle or simply basking in the peaceful ambiance, the pond serves as a captivating centerpiece for outdoor relaxation. Step inside this expansive 4-bedroom, 5-bathroom residence spanning 4565 square feet of meticulously crafted living space. The main level welcomes you into a spacious living/dining area with custom finishes and being a perfect central hub for family gatherings. The kitchen features a gas range, plenty of cabinet space, small pantry, and a center island. Retreat to the luxurious primary bedroom suite on the main level, offering a serene sanctuary complete with a spa-like en-suite bathroom. Three additional bedrooms, one on each level, provide ample accommodation for guests or family members. This exceptional property also has two laundry facilities for added convenience, ensuring effortless day-to-day living. A generator ensures peace of mind during inclement weather or unexpected power outages. With long and short-term rental opportunities permitted, this home presents a lucrative investment opportunity for those seeking to capitalize on the thriving vacation rental market. Whether you're looking for a full-time residence, a vacation retreat, or an income-generating property, this amazing property offers endless possibilities. A 2-story Amish built garage/workshop adds additional functionality with room to store an ATV, tools, and much more. Conveniently located near the Blue Ridge Parkway, residents enjoy easy access to hiking trails, scenic overlooks, & outdoor recreational opportunities.
